# Styling & Design System (PWA)

## Mobile-First (mandatory)

Write base classes for mobile screens first. Add breakpoint prefixes only to override for larger viewports.

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
<div className="flex flex-col gap-3 p-4 md:flex-row md:gap-6 md:p-8">

// ❌ BAD — desktop-first
<div className="hidden md:flex">
```

## Tailwind Rules

- **No arbitrary values:** `w-[312px]`, `text-[13px]`, `mt-[7px]` are forbidden. Use the Tailwind scale.
- **No inline styles:** `style={{ color: '#fff' }}` is forbidden. Map to a Tailwind token.
- **Spacing scale:** Use `p-4`, `gap-3`, `mt-6` — multiples of 4 by default.
- **Colors:** Only use tokens defined in `tailwind.config.js` and the shadcn CSS variables (`bg-card`, `text-foreground`, `border`, etc.).

```tsx
// ✅ Design-system tokens
<div className="bg-card text-card-foreground border rounded-xl shadow-sm p-4">

// ❌ Hard-coded colors
<div className="bg-[#1a1a2e] text-[#eee]">
```

## Touch Targets (PWA)

Interactive elements in mobile must have a minimum touch area of 44×44px.

```tsx
// ✅ Minimum touch target
<button className="min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px] flex items-center justify-center p-3">

// Use active: prefix for mobile press feedback
<button className="active:scale-95 transition-transform">
```

## Accessibility (A11y)

- Images: always descriptive `alt` text.
- Icon-only buttons/links: `aria-label` is required.
- Heading hierarchy: `h1 → h2 → h3` — never skip levels.
- Focusable elements: must be reachable via keyboard (`tabIndex={0}` for non-native elements).
- Status / loading regions: use `aria-live="polite"` for dynamic content updates.

```tsx
// ✅ Icon button
<button aria-label="Fechar modal" onClick={handleClose}>
  <X className="size-5" />
</button>

// ✅ Live region for async feedback
<p aria-live="polite" className="sr-only">
  {isLoading ? 'Carregando...' : ''}
</p>
```

## Component Variants

Use `cva` (class-variance-authority) for components with multiple visual states instead of conditional string concatenation.

```tsx
import { cva } from 'class-variance-authority';

const badgeVariants = cva(
  'inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium',
  {
    variants: {
      status: {
        pendente:  'bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800',
        conferido: 'bg-green-100 text-green-800',
        avaria:    'bg-red-100 text-red-800',
      },
    },
  }
);
```
